	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have a game that requires CNROM to be put into a cart.  The thing is, the game is 128k prg/chr.  CNROM only takes 28 pin chips.  Is there an alternative wiring diagram for this that is not on the site here?   Thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
