	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />PRG on CNROM and its clones is only 32 KiB, and CHR on official CNROM is no larger than 32 KiB.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
