	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What I mean is, the PRG and CHR of the game I want to put onto a cart are 128k (actual file size) each.
<br />
<br />There is not a 28 pin Eprom that will take this size of file, and CNROM games are 28 pin.  
<br />
<br />So I was wondering, is there a way to hook up the 32 pin chips to the CNROM board, Kinda like the UNROM does (it leaves pins 1, 2, 31, 32 not connected to the board, but wired elsewhere)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


